Programmer: Maxime Charlebois


ctint

COMPILING:

to compile, simply do:
$ make

note that you need lapack and blas. Edit the makefile to link with correct library (now it is designed to compile with mkl on my computer).

EXAMPLES:

3 examples files can be found in the example directory. For now, only the directory dmft have been tested correctly. 
Go in one of these directories and type ./scrip.sh to run an example from iteration 0.

TEST: 

you can compile test (to do: documentation)

